snippet.title: Candy Boo: Tournament Edition
snippet.description:
Visit: https://www.megafans.com/
Make a dash for Candy Boo: Tournament Edition!
Candy Booo: Tournament Edition is the most funny puzzle match 3 game.

Pop up super candy like bubbles.
Use match 3 combinations to make candy crushes.
Special combinations (4 in line, 5 in line, T and L shaped combinations) create super candy.
Combine super candy to see super crashes!.

This Super Candy Story is the most addictive Match 3 puzzle game with lots
of challenging puzzles for you.

If you crushed all the jelly slots in certain number of moves, you will receive a bonus game with multiplication of candy scores. Level up. .

Download, Install and Play. Invite your friends, Have fun!
